cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.DS

The paper discusses a distributed reasoning system that involves reasoning locally and soliciting peers for additional information. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The system also deals with data management and semantic web, which could fall under databases (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper includes an experimental analysis of the scalability of the system, which could also fall under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
